OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FThe Supreme Court has ruled that parts
OL,7,Fof a law that ended police
OL,8,Finvestigations and inquests related to
OL,9,Fthe Troubles, did not lead to victims'
OL,10,Frights being diminished.
OL,12,FThe 2023 Legacy Act was introduced by
OL,13,Fthe previous Conservative government
OL,14,Fand offered conditional immunity for
OL,15,Fperpetrators of some Troubles crimes
OL,16,Fin exchange for co-operation with a
OL,17,Fnew body, the Independent Commission
OL,18,Ffor Reconciliation and Information
OL,19,FRecovery (ICRIR), which would oversee
OL,20,Finvestigations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
