OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FThe Labour Government has since
OL,7,Fintroduced a new Bill to Parliament to
OL,8,Foverhaul the Act.
OL,10,FMPs have already voted to repeal the
OL,11,Fconditional immunity provision and
OL,12,Fscrap a bar on future legacy
OL,13,Fcompensation cases as the new Bill is
OL,14,Fstill being debated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
