OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's High Court and the
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Court of Appeal
OL,8,F(NICA) had both previously found that
OL,9,Fparts of the Act were incompatible
OL,10,Fwith human rights and also undermined
OL,11,Fthe rights of victims in breach of the
OL,12,FWindsor Framework, which was signed
OL,13,Ffollowing the UK's leaving the EU.
OL,15,FThe framework states that the
OL,16,Fgovernment must ensure that various
OL,17,Frights and entitlements in Northern
OL,18,FIreland, enshrined by the 1998 Good
OL,19,FFriday Agreement, cannot be diminished.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
