CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FIn a ruling on Thursday, five Supreme
OL,7,FCourt justices unanimously allowed the
OL,8,FGovernment's challenge.
OL,10,FLords Reed, Hodge, Lloyd-Jones,
OL,11,FHamblen and Stephens said in their 77-
OL,12,Fpage judgment that four victims were
OL,13,F"unable to establish that the 2023 Act
OL,14,Fled to a diminution of rights".
OL,16,FReading a summary of the judgment at
OL,17,Fthe court in London, Lord Stephens
OL,18,Fsaid that around 1,200 killings during
OL,19,Fthe Troubles remain unsolved.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
