OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FThe Legacy Act was introduced despite
OL,7,Fopposition from all the main political
OL,8,Fparties at Stormont and the Irish
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FThe Supreme Court was told in court
OL,12,Fdocuments that 20 legal challenges
OL,13,Fwere launched against the legislation
OL,14,F"within days" of its introduction,
OL,15,Fwith the case of Ms Dillon, Mr McEvoy,
OL,16,FMs Hughes and Ms McManus heard in 2023.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
