PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FMs Dillon's husband, Seamus, was shot
OL,7,Fdead by loyalists in Dungannon in
OL,8,F1997, and Ms Hughes' husband, Anthony,
OL,9,Fwas killed by security forces in
OL,10,FLoughgall in 1987.
OL,12,FMr McEvoy and Ms McManus' father,
OL,13,FJames, were both seriously injured
OL,14,Fwhen attacked by loyalists in 1992 in
OL,15,FKilcoo and Belfast, respectively.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
