CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FIn February 2024, Mr Justice Colton
OL,7,Ffound that the conditional immunity
OL,8,Fprovision within the Act breached
OL,9,Fvictims' human rights, and that parts
OL,10,Fof the Act could be disapplied under
OL,11,Fthe Windsor Framework.
OL,13,FThe government did not appeal against
OL,14,Fthe findings on human rights but did
OL,15,Fchallenge other aspects of the
OL,16,Fjudgment, including those about the
OL,17,Fframework.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FIts appeal was unsuccessful, with the
OL,7,FNICA ruling in September 2024 that the
OL,8,FAct created a "diminution" of rights
OL,9,Ffor victims.
OL,11,FIt also found that a government veto
OL,12,Fpower over what sensitive material can
OL,13,Fbe disclosed to bereaved families by
OL,14,Fthe ICRIR was unlawful as it prevented
OL,15,Fits investigations from being
OL,16,Fcompatible with human rights.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FBut Sir James Eadie KC, for the
OL,7,Fgovernment, said in written
OL,8,Fsubmissions for the three-day Supreme
OL,9,FCourt hearing that the NICA's finding
OL,10,Fon the effect of the framework was not
OL,11,Fits "true legal effect".
OL,13,FHe also said that the veto power "only
OL,14,Frelates to disclosure of sensitive
OL,15,Finformation that would risk
OL,16,Fprejudicing national security" and
OL,17,Fthat it was "not objectionable in
OL,18,Fprinciple, or incompatible, for that
OL,19,Fdecision to be taken by the executive".
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@WO]uD@bOUxD@^O]yD@MOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FJohn Larkin KC, for the victims, said
OL,7,Fthe findings of the courts were
OL,8,F"plainly correct" and that there was
OL,9,F"no error of law" by the NICA.
OL,11,FHe continued that the ICRIR was
OL,12,F"structurally incapable of ensuring
OL,13,Fthat the next of kin or victim must be
OL,14,Finvolved in the procedure to the
OL,15,Fextent necessary to safeguard his or
OL,16,Fher legitimate interests".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@QO]qD@AOUqD@QO]tD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FBut the five justices also allowed the
OL,7,FGovernment's challenge against the
OL,8,FNICA ruling related to the ICRIR,
OL,9,Fstating that the victims "cannot
OL,10,Festablish" that the Government's veto
OL,11,Fpower would mean the body "will lack
OL,12,Findependence", and that even if it
OL,13,Fdid, they could not prove that this
OL,14,Fwould "result in there being an
OL,15,Fineffective investigation".
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@JO]sD@[OUtD@MO]vD@GOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
