PN,44213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FThe Act was already being reviewed by
OL,7,Fthe time of the Supreme Court hearing,
OL,8,Fwith the Labour Government, in co-
OL,9,Foperation with the Irish government,
OL,10,Fpresenting the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FTroubles Bill to Parliament last year.
OL,13,FThis would repeal and replace the
OL,14,FLegacy Act and end the immunity
OL,15,Fscheme, instead installing a reformed
OL,16,FLegacy Commission with enhanced powers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
