SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778170272
OL,3,CTroubles legacy law did not diminish
OL,4,Cvictims' rights, Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FWhile the Bill has not been fully
OL,7,Fdebated or passed by Parliament, it
OL,8,Fwill continue to be debated in the
OL,9,Fnext parliamentary session after MPs
OL,10,Fbacked a carry-over motion.
